{"tid":1058573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生活上見過最聰明既女人係點","createTime":"2019-03-12T15:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T15:39:15.000Z","uid":172990,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"204d5b10077dfc22924b79508d152e9993e2a0a6","tid":1058573,"uid":172990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"公司活動 識咗個 大我十年 高我三級既女同事<br />\n嗰晚都傾咗幾耐偈 又飲酒又跳舞<br />\n嗰晚有一個因公事悶悶不樂嘅同事 佢又一直好耐心咁開解佢<br />\n派對之後第二日佢都有Whatsapp我傾咗兩句<br />\n<br />\n佢做生命科學嘅法律工作 主要做藥物專利權<br />\n名牌大學嘅化學系出身 做咗陣研究之後先轉做律師<br />\n<br />\n佢提起自己有單案 幫個客推翻咗一個藥物專利權<br />\n阻止咗市場壟斷 令到醫療界每年慳幾百萬<br />\n佢話覺得好自豪 可以幫到人<br />\n我好欣賞佢對工作嗰份熱誠同自信心<br />\n<br />\n佢 聰明 性格好<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚之後一直都諗住佢 念念不忘<br />\n唉 沉左船 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聰明既女人真係好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee3b36fff6509e32b5fbb412c188cce758aaf3c","tid":1058573,"uid":191352,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f0e3ed526dfe891d8355e3b79d9367712b87508","tid":1058573,"uid":172990,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"識親大部份都係無主見，跟風，無理性可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe1ee00da97b06e5c5fd9f0afe9f91ecda6ebe3","tid":1058573,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79bccaf18d31257a3eb6a70c5aa6b90a0c221444","tid":1058573,"uid":172990,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"由18歲個年開始覺得 女仔樣靚好快厭<br />\n但聰明既女人真係玩極唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0341b2cf26d73c2641967eeeff22add838a545","tid":1058573,"uid":89558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"